<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">If you apply naive logic, you might conclude: </span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;Marketing causes returns. If we stop marketing, our return rate will drop to zero!&quot;</span></span>
